{
  "texts": [
    "Providers of GAI services could jeopardize users' privacy by mishandling their data.",
    "This danger is especially evident when using GAI tools may lead to data breaches that expose sensitive information.",
    "In addition, GAI systems are increasingly vulnerable to cyber-attacks.",
    "These systems can be targeted in different ways such as introducing harmful data or exploiting system weaknesses to gain unauthorized access.",
    "The ethical and security considerations surrounding GAI tools are significant in academic research and peer review processes and need to be addressed to ensure the confidentiality of researchers' scholarly work (Alshami et al., 2023; Anghelescu et al., 2023; Bond et al., 2024; Mollaki, 2024; Nguyen et al., 2024)."
  ]
}